text: Kalininskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltymanovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 9 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Iglino, 12 km from Kaltymanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kalininskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan
